	<div style="text-align:right;">
		SILVA FILHO, Samuel Giatti da<sup>1</sup>; COELHO, Leandro Dos Santos<sup>2</sup>; FREIRE, Roberto Zanetti<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
